{"tid":2489431,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"彭定康夥同過百名跨黨派上議院下議院議員去信英國首相，要求英國制裁香港官員及陳全國","createTime":"2021-04-15T02:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T14:18:22.000Z","uid":28114,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f2c1273e8bfe969d3d57d3c206d6a099d24c50a9","tid":2489431,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:56:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hk_watch/status/1382413500824305666?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhk_watch%2Fstatus%2F1382413500824305666%3Fs%3D21&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=5e12c479\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhk_watch%2Fstatus%2F1382413500824305666%3Fs%3D21&h=353c507e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hk_watch/status/1382413500824305666?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"9be85fba8e3d04f8314dd2df78f8911713f99af2","tid":2489431,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:57:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-56749966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-56749966&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=9eb41253\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-56749966&h=eeb85e87\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-56749966</a>"},{"pid":"f32ddf3d385a73c1953149c714e99fa8341dd7d0","tid":2489431,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8ff5475212dcd0ba946afbeb7703f84b95c7d7","tid":2489431,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516aed34d27c5a8af4e29fa3ac77e49fb69d9166","tid":2489431,"uid":92811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f12b82c22ae365bece7709c44a4e5199ff0fd6f","tid":2489431,"uid":290404,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:15:49.000Z","msg":"前港督彭定康與英國過百名跨黨派國會議員，聯署去信首相約翰遜，要求英國政府引用《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》，制裁被指打壓香港民主運動的官員及實體，並且對新疆黨委書記陳全國等被指侵害新疆維吾爾人權的官員，實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n彭定康在信中表示，反對中方上月對多名英國國會議員實施的制裁<strong>，認為中方的制裁反映中國政府的威權主義正在擴張</strong>，他又認為，英國與中國的所謂「黃金時代」已經過去，敦促英國政府以跨部門方式，盡快檢視策略，以應對中國政府對自由世界帶來的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部在上月底，宣布制裁英方9名人員和4個實體，他們涉嫌惡意傳播謊言和虛假信息，中方保留採取進一步措施的權利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585874-20210415.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585874-20210415.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=e1df6793\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585874-20210415.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=67b2b451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585874-20210415.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"75e30b87aaeb403c0068a3d4dcb77e2548de403b","tid":2489431,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329979165ccd1a74fc1d762eac9f5a67aab1ba4d","tid":2489431,"uid":79005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8c2fc5292d388d3e21c51be0fd65695f1e0cfa","tid":2489431,"uid":126521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T03:17:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66f79cba03791451a22e2543